      "level": 1,
      "category": "card",
      "keywords": [],
      "metadata": {
        "card_bg": "#134e4a",
        "card_subtitle": "Yes — both a mirror and a window. A mirror to your present; and, like a face seen in still water, a window onto what you might imagine. The cards don't know your future — they cast new light into the structures of this moment, in new language, opening the imagination to other possibilities.",
